<span class="gutter">  17:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">input</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">type</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">radio</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">name</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">choice</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">fish</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>Fish
<span class="gutter">  18:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">input</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">type</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">radio</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">name</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">choice</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">steak</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>Steak
<span class="gutter">  19:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">input</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">type</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">radio</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">name</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">choice</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">yogurt</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>Yogurt
<span class="gutterH">  20:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">p</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  21:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">b</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>Choose a work place:<span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">b</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span> <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">br</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  22:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">input</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">type</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">checkbox</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">name</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">place1</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">LA</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>Los Angeles
<span class="gutter">  23:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">br</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  24:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">input</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">type</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">checkbox</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">name</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">place2</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">SJ</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>San Jose
<span class="gutterH">  25:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">br</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  26:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">input</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">type</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">checkbox</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">name</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">place3</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span>
<span class="gutter">  27:</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">SF</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">Checked</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>San Francisco
<span class="gutter">  28:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">p</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  29:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">b</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>Choose a vacation spot: <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">b</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutterH">  30:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">select</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">name</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">location</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  31:</span>     <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">option</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">selected</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">hawaii</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span> Hawaii
<span class="gutter">  32:</span>     <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">option</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">bali</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>Bali
<span class="gutter">  33:</span>     <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">option</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">maine</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>Maine
<span class="gutter">  34:</span>     <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">option</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">paris</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>Paris
<span class="gutterH">  35:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">select</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  36:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">p</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  37:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">input</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">type</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">submit</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">submit</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  38:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">p</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  39:</span>   <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">input</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">type</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">reset</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">value</span><span class="syntax18">=</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax13">clear</span><span class="syntax13">&quot;</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutterH">  40:</span>  <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">form</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  41:</span>  <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">hr</span><span class="syntax17"> </span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  42:</span> <span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">body</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span>
<span class="gutter">  43:</span><span class="syntax17">&lt;</span><span class="syntax17">/</span><span class="syntax17">html</span><span class="syntax17">&gt;</span></span>
</PRE>
</div>
</small></blockquote>
<p>
Line 7 is the beginning of a &lt;form&gt; tag that specifies where the browser
will send the input data and the method that will be used to process it.
</p><p>
The default method is the GET method. When the data is submitted, the PHP script
(or some other program, such as CGI script) will be executed by the server.
</p><p>
In this example, the PHP script is stored in the same directory as the form file
</p><p>
The field on line 9 has an input type of text box that will hold up to 50 characters.
When the user types text into the text box, that text will be stored in the
user-defined name value, namestring.
</p><p>
If assigned a value attribute, the text field can take a default; that is, text
that appears in the text box when it is initially displayed by the browser.
</p><p>
The field on line 2 is a text area, which is similar to the text field, but will
allow input that spans multiple lines.
</p><p>
The textarea tag will produce a rectangle with dimensions in rows and columns
(5 rows by 50 columns) and an optional default value (I was born...).
On lines 16-19 the input type is a list of radio buttons. Only one button can be
selected. The input type has two attributes: a type and a name.
</p><p>
The value of the name attribute "choice", for example, will be assigned "burger"
if the user clicks on the Hamburger option, choice=burger is passed onto the PHP
program. If the user selects Fish, choice=fish will be assigned to the query string,
and so on.
</p><p>
These key–value pairs are used to build a query string to pass onto the PHP
program after the Submit button is pressed.
</p><p>
The input type on lines 22-27 is in the form of check boxes. More than one check
box might be selected. The optional default box is already checked.
</p><p>
When the user selects one of the check boxes, the value of the name attribute
will be assigned one of the values from the value attribute; for example,
place1=LA if Los Angeles is checked.
</p><p>
The select tag on lines 30-35 is used to produce a pop-up menu (also called a
drop-down list) or a scrollable list.
</p><p>
The name option is required. It is used to define the name for the set of options.
For a pop-up menu, the size attribute is not necessary; it defaults to 1.
</p><p>
The pop-up menu initially displays one option and expands to a menu when that
option is clicked. Only one selection can be made from the menu.
</p><p>
If a size attribute is given, that many items will be displayed. If the "multiple"
attribute is given (e.g., SELECT MULTIPLE NAME=whatever), the menu appears as a
scrollable list, displaying all of the options.
</p><p>
When the user clicks the Submit button, the PHP script listed in the form's action
attribute will be launched. In this example, the PHP script does not exist, so
an error message is sent to the server's error log and to the browser.
</p><p>
If the Clear button is pressed, all input boxes are reset back to their defaults.
</p><p>
After the user fills out the form, he or she will click the Submit button.
This causes submission of the form.
</p><p>
The browser will collect all the input that was entered, URL encode it, package
it up, and send it to the web server, which in turn will send it to the script
listed in the action attribute of the &lt;form&gt; tag.
</p><p>
The table describes a list of form input types and their possible attributes.
</p><p>
Table: Form Input Types
</p>
